Do voices carry valid information about a speakerâ€™s personality?

Julia Stern, Christoph Schild, Benedict C. Jones, Lisa M. DeBruine, Amanda Hahn, David A. Puts, Ingo Zettler, Tobias L. Kordsmeyer, David Feinberg, Dan Zamfir, Lars Penke, & Ruben C. Arslan

2/7/2020

Results

  • Codebook: The codebook contains metadata, means, missingness, correlations, sex differences, age trends, and further information on all variables in the study. We also provide a codebook with unstandardised variables.
  • Preregistered tests
  • Exploratory analyses and robustness checks

Voice pitch and formants

To hear different voice pitches and formants, click the initials of the authors of our study below. Youâ€™ll hear each of us speak the letters â€œA-E-I-O-Uâ€.

Reproducibility

This repository uses the renv package to make it easier to rerun analyses using the same setup and package versions that were used to create them.

Hereâ€™s a classical session info.
